4) Write a Python program to perform sum of three given integers. 
  However, if any of the two values are equal then sum will be zero (eg : 2+1+1 = 0)

a=input("Enter a")
b=input("Enter b")
c=input("Enter c")
d=0
if(a==b | a==c | b==c):print("sum= "+str(d))
else :print("sum= "+str(a+b+c))


